Traffic Stops in Hartford, Connecticut

Dasha Metropolitansky

April 1, 2019

Answering questions about the data

There were a total of 729 arrests made in Hartford.

There are 669 unique locations at which white individuals less than age 30 were issued citations.

The first arrest of a female in the South End district was on April 8, 2015.

Officer 09739d95d7 has made the most stops in districts with “South” in their name.
